<h2>Overview</h2>

<p><a href="https://orderprepped.com" rel="noopener noreferrer">Prepped</a> is an end-to-end SaaS platform for meal prep companies, catering services, personal chefs, and food delivery businesses. It handles the full lifecycle from customer ordering through production planning, subscription management, and last-mile delivery — replacing the patchwork of spreadsheets, generic e-commerce tools, and manual processes that most food businesses rely on.</p>

<p>The platform serves operators globally. The meal prep and catering industries are inherently local in execution but global in structure — the operational challenges of a meal prep operator in London, São Paulo, or Seoul are identical to those in Chicago. Prepped's infrastructure is built to serve all of them: timezone-aware scheduling, multi-region support, i18n-ready interfaces, and a delivery architecture that integrates both proprietary fleet management and third-party logistics providers.</p>

<p>Pricing is pay-as-you-grow with zero upfront costs — a business processing 50 orders a week pays only for those orders. A catering company scaling to thousands pays a lower per-order rate. The model is designed so that the platform becomes more affordable exactly as the business grows.</p>

